# ─── Vercel Deployment Notes ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The crawler cannot run on Vercel (serverless, read-only filesystem, no Playwright).
# Workflow:
#   1. Run `npm run crawl` locally
#   2. Commit the generated files (data/, public/leagues/)
#   3. Push → Vercel auto-deploys with the pre-built pages
#
# Because of this, data/ and public/leagues/ MUST be committed (not ignored).
# Only images/ is large enough to consider storing elsewhere (e.g. a CDN).

# Uncomment the lines below ONLY if you move images to an external CDN:
# images/leagues/

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
